title: Left of Black with Jason Moran
description:
Left of Black host Dr. Mark Anthony Neal sits down with musician Jason Moran to discuss his work, collaborating with family, and his influences.

Jason Moran is a jazz pianist, composer, and educator. Jason is in residency with the band, The Bandwagon at Duke University, https://dukeperformances.duke.edu/events/jason-moran-the-bandwagon/

Dr. Neal teaches Black Popular Culture in the Department of African and African-American Studies at Duke University.
fulltitle: Left of Black with Jason Moran
uploader: John Hope Franklin Center at Duke University
channel: John Hope Franklin Center at Duke University
